Check out the newest miniatures coming out for Infinity and Warcrow!
https://store.corvusbelli.com/en/coming-soon

LIVE NEXT WEEK!!! Catacombs of the Blessed Dead Official Trench Crusade Terrain and EonsOfBattle Miniatures available digitally and physically! Follow to find out more about the project and get a free gift with your pledge! It is launching next week! https://gamefound.com/en/projects/eonsofbattle/catacombs-of-the-blessed-dead

Get The Chaotic Cemetery Terrain Pack or any of our other previous 3D model packs on our website: https://eonsofbattle.com/ You can get one 3D model pack FREE with the EOB Terrain tier and above! AND we will now print terrain, bits and base toppers for you!!! Check it out: https://eonsofbattle.com/collections/physical-prints 

In this episode of Models and Memories #232 Jay talks about being at the Nova Open, having a board at the Trench Crusade Booth and What Games Workshop and Infinity are coming out with soon! We have new videos every Monday, Wed
title: New Minis! First Time at the Nova Open!
